  "title": "BIM MODELLER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Your Role</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To construct 3D model and prepare shop drawings for submission to the authorities and for construction using BIM software</li>\n  <li>Update 3D model according to latest information provided and ensure accuracy of shop drawings</li>\n  <li>Monitor and inform Project Design Team on clashes</li>\n  <li>Support Project Design Team in managing RFIs</li>\n  <li>Achieve the drawing submission schedule</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>The Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess a Degree in Civil Engineering/ Architecture/ Mechanical or Electrical Engineering with minimum 3 years relevant working experience in the local construction industry (contractor firm preferred)</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Revit (Architecture, MEP, Structure), Tekla and MicroStation – AECOsim</li>\n  <li>Experienced in production of shop drawings</li>\n</ul>",
